<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Lutz</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-04 07:14:47</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Can be purchased from one of the vendors in the temple of life courtyard in Qeynos.<BR>
<BR>
This has also been used as a powerlevelling tactic. High level cleric beats the crap out of a critter, roots, atone, and lil guy hits it and gets full XP.<BR>
<BR>
Dont know if this still works, I have better things to do then PL lazy ass newbies.  =)</font></td></tr></table>
