<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>K this spell really rocks when you are being pleveled by someone, especially being a cleric and you cant meelee for crap.  All you do is let whoever is plevelling u smack the crap out of the mob...then when it is vlow health you shout ATONING...your pleveler stops attacking the mob..you cast..if the mob stops attacking moentarily and it says mob has clamed down..you nuke it..kill it and get full xp...this spell works very well because now its not noly druids that can plevel you really well (DS and regen etc)..you dont need that.even a high lvl tank can just smack away and you get the xp...all u have to do is sit and med thru the fight.....60 mana for the atone (120 if u need to recast) and a nuke ..wrath or expel at lvl 34...boom xp..<BR>
Once atone has been cast the mob will agrro pretty quckly again because u will probably be standing right next to it...HOWEVER the ultimate pleveling i found is still with druids....in wolfie form u can cast atone and the mob will stop attacking completely and wander back to its spawn spot..so there ya go...any questions..just ask./...oh yeah..ps i dont get plveveld often...only got pleveled like 1 bub of xp for like 30 mins...so pls no spamming about blah blah pleveling blah blah....<BR>
